<H1> Demetrius: On Style</H1> 
<B> &nbsp; &nbsp; - translated by W. Rhys Roberts</B>
<BR><BR><HR> 
 
<P> <I>This translation is no longer available in its original location on the web at classicpersuasion.org, and therefore it has been copied here for ease of reference, with minimal alterations. &nbsp; Little is known about Demetrius, apart from his name; and even his approximate date (perhaps 1st or 2nd century A.D.) is uncertain. The Greek text of his treatise can be found at <A HREF="http://www.perseus.tufts.edu/hopper/text?doc=Perseus%3Atext%3A2008.01.0630%3Abook%3D1%3Achapter%3D1">Perseus</A>.</I>

