<p><i>This e-version of W. Rhys Roberts' translation of Demetrius <b>On Style</b> was adapted from: 
Demetrius On style: the Greek text of Demetrius <b>De Elocutione</b>
edited after the Paris manuscript with introd., translation, facsimiles, etc. by W. Rhys Roberts
(Cambridge, at the University Press: 1902), pp. 67-207. This is only the translation
from Robert's edition, and does not include his scholarly notes or commentary. Some of Roberts'
notes have been converted to in-line links and modified to reflect reference style at the Perseus Project.
</i></p>


